<p>At CD’s request HBD has traced the quotation; it is on regeneration from Charles White in W. B. Carpenter’s <hi rend="italic">Comparative physiology</hi> (1854), p. 480.</p>  
<p>Is gratified that CD thinks some of the arguments in his book [<hi rend="italic">Lectures on the germs of disease</hi> (1861)] are satisfactory.</p> 
